    "Text modality, enhanced by natural language processing techniques like sentiment analysis, offers an added layer of emotional context, supporting the effectiveness of MER systems (see Fig. 6).Figure 4 also categorizes the benchmarking metrics into two primary groups based on their coverage in review studies.",
    "Metrics in green are well-covered, representing a common pattern followed by most studies.",
    "In contrast, the metrics in orange indicate research gaps, as they have not been addressed by many studies.",
    "Figure 8 provides a Fig. 6 The coverage of cues within the study set with cues highlighted in red indicating the highest coverage.",
    "Among the physiological signals group, EEG and ECG exhibit the most extensive coverage."
